Definition: butt welding by creating an electric arc between the two pieces which melts and joins them
Example: used for joining segments of metal pipe
Synonyms: flash_butt_welding, butt_welding, butt, welding, by, creating, an, electric, arc, between, the, two, pieces, which, melts, and, joins, them, used, for, joining, segments, of, metal, pipe
Category: noun.act
